properties.headline: Small Craft Advisory issued February 14 at 4:05AM EST until February 16 at 10:00AM EST by NWS Melbourne FL
properties.description:
* WHAT...North winds 15 to 20 kt with gusts up to 30 kt and seas
7 to 10 feet expected.

* WHERE...Sebastian Inlet to Jupiter Inlet 0-20 nm and Sebastian
Inlet to Jupiter Inlet 20-60 nm.

* WHEN...From 10 PM this evening to 10 AM EST Sunday.

* IMPACTS...Conditions will be hazardous to small craft.
properties.instruction:
Wind and wave conditions will be hazardous for small craft.
Inexperienced mariners, especially those operating smaller
vessels, should avoid navigating in these conditions.

NWSheadline: SMALL CRAFT ADVISORY IN EFFECT FROM 10 PM THIS EVENING TO 10 AM EST SUNDAY
